How to create reports?

A single categorical variable

report_counts(data, sd_geschlecht)

Geschlecht

Plot

Table
Geschlecht n p
weiblich 40 40%
mnnlich 60 59%
divers 1 1%

A cross table

data %>% 
  filter(sd_geschlecht != "divers") %>% 
  report_counts(in_adoption, sd_geschlecht, prop="rows")
